<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= providerLabel %> 로그인 준비중 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3ef;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #111111;
      --text: #1f1f1f;
      --muted: #6f6a63;
      --line: rgba(17,17,17,0.08);
      --gold: #9d8660;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --max: 1280px;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--black);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 16px;
    }

    header {
      background: rgba(245, 243, 239, 0.88);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .header-inner {
      min-height: 82px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 82px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 0 70px;
    }

    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 680px;
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 30px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 42px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 38px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .info-box {
      margin: 24px 0 26px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .info-box strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .info-box span {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      min-width: 180px;
      height: 54px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .btn-dark {
      background: var(--black);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-light {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }

      .header-actions {
        display: none;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 28px 20px;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 30px;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">DAMORE OFFICIAL ONLINE STORE</div>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
          <span class="brand-logo">DAMORE</span>
          <span class="brand-sub">the more, the mood</span>
        </a>

        <div class="header-actions">
          <a href="/auth">로그인 / 회원가입</a>
          <a href="/order/lookup">주문조회</a>
          <a href="/cart">장바구니 <%= typeof cartCount !== 'undefined' ? cartCount : 0 %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Social Login</div>
        <h1><%= providerLabel %> 로그인은 준비중입니다</h1>
        <p>
          현재는 이메일 로그인 / 회원가입을 먼저 사용하고,
          나중에 <%= providerLabel %> 소셜로그인을 실제 연동할 수 있도록 구조만 먼저 만들어둔 상태입니다.
        </p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong>현재 상태</strong>
          <span>
            <%= providerLabel %> 버튼은 UI와 진입 라우트까지는 연결되어 있고,
            실제 로그인 연동(API / 앱 등록 / Redirect URI / 검수)은 다음 단계에서 붙이면 됩니다.
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-group">
          <a href="/login" class="btn btn-dark">이메일 로그인</a>
          <a href="/register" class="btn btn-light">이메일 회원가입</a>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-group" style="margin-top:12px;">
          <a href="/auth" class="btn btn-light">이전으로 돌아가기</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>